snippet.title: Burly Men at Sea - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to PC/Mac and mobile on September 29th, Burly Men at Sea is a folktale about a trio of large, bearded fishermen who step away from the ordinary to seek adventure. Pre-order from the Humble Store: http://humblebundle.com/store/p/burlymenatsea_storefront

Wishlist on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/403290
Add on Itch.io: http://brainbrain.itch.io/burlymenatsea

Sign up for an occasional email in a bottle: burlymenatsea.com
